{
  "stem": "7273.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wasn't allowed to travel, so I stayed overnight with my grandparents, which was big fun for me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had-- I loved them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my father was deeply religious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But not religious so far that he ran with the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I remember every morning he laid his tefillin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And was strictly kosher with our household.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all the holidays, of course, were celebrated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But-- like, in my township in Katowice, when there were Jewish holidays, the High Holidays I'm speaking, the town was dead.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All shops were closed, and there wasn't any life, because most shop owners were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Say, 50%.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Half of it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a very Jewish town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Approximately of 100,000.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Jewish people kept very much together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the center.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was mixed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Also, the place I lived in was mixed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look, before the war, say, it-- it changed all since Hitler was on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was already before the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This relationship with German people changed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Say, '36.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember even in school, I remember, that the girls being on holidays-- mostly after holidays when they came back from Germany-- we could feel-- we were five Jewish girls in my class-- so we could feel this strangeness.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, they-- they were quite different.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Entirely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because it was a border town, and it was very German, especially through that-- that I belonged to this language, to this language group.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I felt it very much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we just had to carry on, because there was only one German high school.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
